{"tid":1926971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國「物競天擇免疫法」擬讓6成人染病 惹議後政策髮夾彎","createTime":"2020-03-15T12:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T20:34:56.000Z","uid":78519,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e9b8786e0b384daaf1197b6183962b405ae718","tid":1926971,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/202003151146245841_08610.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F202003151146245841_08610.jpg&h=4b74aba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">英國首相強生12日在唐寧街首相官邸召開記者會，將新冠肺炎應對計畫提升到「延緩」階段。當時強生還表達不希望禁止運動賽事，但相隔不過一天時間，就有消息人士放風，指內閣大臣準備禁止運動賽事和音樂會等大型集會，最快下周末生效。（歐新社）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/202003151146245882_AG096.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F202003151146245882_AG096.jpg&h=d07c97ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">倫敦民眾出於恐慌心態，14日一家超市的民生物品幾乎被搶購一空。（Getty Images）</span><br />\n<br />\n據英國衛生部門統計，14日新增342例確診新冠肺炎，累計1140例、死亡21例。儘管歐洲疫情緊繃，英國早前的防疫措施卻不禁止大型集會、並要輕症患者不要就醫等，被解讀為採「物競天擇防疫法」，希望全國約六成民眾染病痊癒後，形成普遍的群體免疫力。<br />\n<br />\n英國呼籲居家隔離的輕症病人不要上醫院或藥房，醫療單位也不會篩檢這些患者，因為資源要留給重症病人。而年長者為高危險群，當局建議他們盡量不要出門，也不要參加任何郵輪假期。<br />\n<br />\n英國「衛報」指出，政府看似已放棄遏阻疫情，改採一種連某些專家都覺得過於大膽的防疫手段。英國採取「群體免疫」防疫政策，意即讓國內達到一定程度的染病人口，從而獲得對新型冠狀病毒免疫，然後就不會再傳染給其他未染病的人。期程是趕在下次冬季來臨前，利用夏天這幾個月達到目標。<br />\n<br />\n專家表示，要想達成群體免疫，英國需要約60%甚至70%的民眾染病且痊癒後獲得免疫力。然而，利用這種方法因應尚無疫苗的新型冠狀病毒大流行，許多專家憂心是否真有成效。<br />\n<br />\n台灣前衛生署長楊志良將此法稱為「物競天擇防疫法」。他表示，英國的物競天擇防疫法，是防疫上截然不同的思考模式，目前採取物競天擇防疫法的還有瑞典，瑞典救年輕不救老年患者。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大型集會禁令 最快下周生效</span></strong><br />\n英國首相強生12日記者會上，將新冠肺炎應對計畫提升到「延緩」階段，但不希望禁止運動賽事，表示停賽對防疫「效果甚微」，也未呼籲停課。但不到一天後，首相官邸就暗示，準備禁止運動賽事和音樂會等大型集會，最快下周末生效，以減輕緊急勤務部門的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n世衛組織（WHO）13日強調，若要遏阻病毒就必須採取全盤措施。世衛記者會數小時後，各家英媒就接獲爆料，指強生政策髮夾彎，準備在下周末起開始禁止大型公眾活動，以減輕警察和救護單位的負擔。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>英女王 取消2周公開行程</strong></span><br />\n白金漢宮13日也宣布，英國女王將取消未來2周的公開行程，這也是女王即位68年以來，首次因國家危機取消公開行程；英格蘭足球主管單位自主推遲4月3日前的全部賽事，橄欖球、板球和倫敦馬拉松也提前宣布中止，顯然對中央政策不埋單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/202003151146245923_AG097.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F202003151146245923_AG097.jpg&h=48be9a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">英國女王將取消未來2周的公開行程。（路透資料照片）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/202003151146245974_99990.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F202003151146245974_99990.jpg&h=663622e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">英國疫情升高，倫敦街頭已有民眾戴起口罩。（路透）</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6839625/article-%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e3%80%8c%e7%89%a9%e7%ab%b6%e5%a4%a9%e6%93%87%e5%85%8d%e7%96%ab%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8d%e6%93%ac%e8%ae%936%e6%88%90%e4%ba%ba%e6%9f%93%e7%97%85-%e6%83%b9%e8%ad%b0%e5%be%8c%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96/?ref=%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%AD%E9%8F%A2&amp;ismobile=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6839625%2Farticle-%25e8%258b%25b1%25e5%259c%258b%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%2589%25a9%25e7%25ab%25b6%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e6%2593%2587%25e5%2585%258d%25e7%2596%25ab%25e6%25b3%2595%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%2593%25ac%25e8%25ae%25936%25e6%2588%2590%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%259f%2593%25e7%2597%2585-%25e6%2583%25b9%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e5%25be%258c%25e6%2594%25bf%25e7%25ad%2596%2F%3Fref%3D%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%25BA%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%258F%25A2%26ismobile%3Dtrue&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOycF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=ccb0f1cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6839625/article-%e8%8b%b1%e5%9c%8b%e3%80%8c%e7%89%a9%e7%ab%b6%e5%a4%a9%e6%93%87%e5%85%8d%e7%96%ab%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8d%e6%93%ac%e8%ae%936%e6%88%90%e4%ba%ba%e6%9f%93%e7%97%85-%e6%83%b9%e8%ad%b0%e5%be%8c%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96/?ref=%E5%90%84%E5%9C%8B%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E4%B8%AD%E9%8F%A2&amp;ismobile=true</a>"},{"pid":"a0c196aa4904c229084d5698b3c23b3307b8bfdc","tid":1926971,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"髪夾灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18bb5af30b9829556e1a00d971e94f29284eb9f","tid":1926971,"uid":144229,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">據英國衛生部門統計，14日新增342例確診新冠肺炎，累計1140例、死亡21例。儘管歐洲疫情緊繃，英國早前的防疫措施卻不禁止大型集會、並要輕症患者不要就醫等，被解讀為採「物競天擇防疫法」，希望全國約六成民眾染病痊癒後，形成普遍的群體免疫力。</span><br />\nFailed State<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d9e354aa66f270bfc84315f76da7ea3a2e7545","tid":1926971,"uid":3873,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"死淨嗰班就會話we are the chosen"},{"pid":"a7a8bc11686a45be2167c1c373b123a55fa3b88f","tid":1926971,"uid":78519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:04:49.000Z","msg":"Boris 佛系防疫以後傳出要「楢山節考」 正要懲罰支持他的選民？<br />\n&hellip;//其中在英國，首相府的首席科學家，甚至提出，多人染病，自然社會就有免疫力一說，嚇著不少人。<br />\n然後週末英國確診個案激增後，約翰遜似乎無法繼續佛系防疫，於是要宣布新政策了。<br />\n相傳期中一項是，要求70歲以上老人，在家或老人院，隔絕4個月。各大媒體政治記者得知爆料後，自然議論紛紛，負評也不斷。<br />\nElderly could be quarantined for four months in 'wartime-style' mobilisation to combat coronavirus&hellip;<br />\nPeople over 70 will be instructed by the government to stay in strict isolation at home or in care homes for four&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.itv.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.itv.com&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOycF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=df503e54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.itv.com</a><br />\n見到這樣「楢山節考」的政策，我反而想到了去年大選的結果。Yougov 出口民調表示，65歲以上受訪者，64%支持保守黨。// &hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/gausee-寰雨膠事錄/boris-佛系防疫以後傳出要-楢山節考-正要懲罰支持他的選民-6b8fa5997d82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fgausee-%E5%AF%B0%E9%9B%A8%E8%86%A0%E4%BA%8B%E9%8C%84%2Fboris-%E4%BD%9B%E7%B3%BB%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%8C%E5%82%B3%E5%87%BA%E8%A6%81-%E6%A5%A2%E5%B1%B1%E7%AF%80%E8%80%83-%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%81%E6%87%B2%E7%BD%B0%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%BB%96%E7%9A%84%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91-6b8fa5997d82&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOycF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=37eb0446\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/gausee-寰雨膠事錄/boris-佛系防疫以後傳出要-楢山節考-正要懲罰支持他的選民-6b8fa5997d82</a>"},{"pid":"c6daf4fb6578abb8b0ca1ee4f4243274969867bd","tid":1926971,"uid":259813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"其實咁舉棋不定係咪死得仲快"},{"pid":"51250b1b609cb568b37aaf6f521a42cf0b6ee2c5","tid":1926971,"uid":262183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a0c196aa4904c229084d5698b3c23b3307b8bfdc","tid":1926971,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"髪夾灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:06:21.000Z","msg":"條友真係唔識架喎"},{"pid":"609dbb8f0151bfb192fc3225250d94d448994f75","tid":1926971,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:07:00.000Z","msg":"坡狗笑左未"},{"pid":"7b92f80d6b41cc5bdc30bdbfeda56962176812cc","tid":1926971,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"[YouTube戰線][黃頁]我哋係一班整合團隊,最近遇到一樣野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1920237\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1920237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地又比人抄野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地個設計比藍屍抄緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n要幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6440ec8d9f629972c1a2e000c6a1a1864a5402","tid":1926971,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:08:26.000Z","msg":"香港需要Boris Johnson<br />\n<br />\n香港救支狗廢老優先"},{"pid":"0f1c955b136001dbc705baa3e1e4bd37673007b8","tid":1926971,"uid":9542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"如果黎多次大選條友實輸到仆街，未開始抵抗已經放棄左先"},{"pid":"4ecacbd5c8a14e28f54c1a48c24c2620d5fb6b19","tid":1926971,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:13:43.000Z","msg":"強生&amp;強生"},{"pid":"5b7a099ba7798cdf87d10a572875c528d40aec11","tid":1926971,"uid":57397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"英女皇:屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b5d5a2ba1fccbdc7cb3e18faee2f4e6aa48236","tid":1926971,"uid":138609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"講到尾都係錢<br />\n唔想影響經濟<br />\n唔想多洗醫療費<br />\n佛系抗疫佛系治療"},{"pid":"38ca92bc8f0bacdd47a8dbcc9c9c20fd14014f0f","tid":1926971,"uid":165711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:2